01:49.466 --> 01:52.162
Bring out the broads!

01:52.235 --> 01:54.169
Let me at him!
Let me at him!

01:54.237 --> 01:56.228
Somebody throw a net
over this broad.

01:56.306 --> 01:58.206
Did you see him kiss
that fat fucker?

01:58.275 --> 02:00.368
Steve.
I'll always know him as 18.

02:00.443 --> 02:02.206
He, uh-

02:02.279 --> 02:07.410
He was killed by a drunk driver just
a month before he was to graduate.

02:07.484 --> 02:09.418
And-

02:09.485 --> 02:12.478
It's hard when you have
two policemen come in and say,

02:12.555 --> 02:14.819
"Your daughter's dead. "

02:14.891 --> 02:18.258
I op- I opened the door
and I saw 'em standing there,

02:18.328 --> 02:20.762
and I said,
"Mandy's dead, isn't she?"

02:20.830 --> 02:22.730
A mom knows.

02:38.915 --> 02:42.146
All right!

02:42.218 --> 02:45.210
Freddy, he's comin' over here.
You better slide in... a lot.

02:45.288 --> 02:48.587
- He needs half a booth.
- Sunny. How ya doin', Sunny? Everything good?

02:50.627 --> 02:52.561
How 'bout that?
How'd you like to spank it?

02:52.629 --> 02:55.189
- Nice!
- Oh, yeah! But softly.

02:55.265 --> 02:58.257
