- Nice.

02:58.335 --> 03:01.031
My wife,
you know Joan.

03:01.104 --> 03:04.733
We got a step-down living room.
It's like two steps down.

03:04.808 --> 03:07.436
So the bitch don't wanna walk.
She wants me to raise it.

03:07.510 --> 03:09.740
She don't wanna walk down
two steps.

03:09.813 --> 03:12.441
