that we lost.

04:04.801 --> 04:09.704
And...

04:09.773 --> 04:13.641
he was sibling number one.

04:14.677 --> 04:16.644
And...

04:18.248 --> 04:21.081
they, th-they didn't-

04:21.151 --> 04:23.711
Did they forget?
I don't know.

04:26.823 --> 04:28.381
