28:27.929 --> 28:31.592
This fuckin' gun ain't got
no fuckin' clip. You cock.

28:36.638 --> 28:39.106
All right
I get a cigarette?

28:42.177 --> 28:44.111
All right.

28:56.925 --> 28:58.893
You know-

29:01.796 --> 29:04.629
Would you mind closin' the door?
I don't want to wake my parents.

29:12.007 --> 29:14.942
Might fuckin' wake
his fuckin' parents.

29:25.954 --> 29:27.922
When the thing happened,

29:31.960 --> 29:34.554
I wanted to be dead.

29:37.899 --> 29:42.427
But there wasn't-
You know.

29:42.504 --> 29:45.837
I didn't want
your forgiveness.

29:45.907 --> 29:50.003
I didn't think I deserved it.
And I don't think I do.

29:53.481 --> 29:55.449
But...

30:04.559 --> 30:06.527
I guess you, uh...

30:08.063 --> 30:11.055
you've been waitin' for this day
for a long time.

30:11.132 --> 30:13.896
It's all right.
Sit down.

30:18.440 --> 30:20.374
Sit down.

30:21.910 --> 30:25.073
I know it's been
a long wait.

30:25.146 --> 30:28.274
But I'm not goin' anywhere.

30:31.152 --> 30:34.986
I'm not callin' any cops.

30:35.056 --> 30:39.322
I'll just be here,
trying to get on with things.

30:47.869 --> 30:50.030
Would you maybe,
you know-

30:53.208 --> 30:56.939
Would you take
a couple days...

30:57.012 --> 31:00.038
and maybe think about
not takin' my life?

31:00.115 --> 31:03.084
Look.

31:03.151 --> 31:07.884
I'm a jeweler.
I got a jewelry store.

31:07.956 --> 31:12.484
That's all I got.
That's it. That's what I am.

31:12.560 --> 31:15.358
- Understand what I'm talkin' about?
- I think I do.

31:15.430 --> 31:19.890
Shut up! Because you don't.
You don't understand. You don't!

31:22.303 --> 31:24.294
All right.

31:40.522 --> 31:44.219
I'm gonna give you
three days.

